  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-powered threat modeling using STRIDE methodology",
    "Attack tree generation and visualization",
    "DREAD risk scoring for threat assessment",
    "Specialized support for GenAI and Agentic AI applications",
    "Multi-modal analysis with architecture diagrams",
    "GitHub repository analysis",
    "Multiple LLM provider support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Mistral, Groq)",
    "Local model hosting via Ollama and LM Studio",
